{"tid":1999003,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國不滿美台就疫情通話及支持台灣參加世衛大會","createTime":"2020-05-02T23:54:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T16:15:09.000Z","uid":130626,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"1164b04d4f22acb338fc671df4c022c1aeb02ead","tid":1999003,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T23:54:08.000Z","msg":"中國批評美國衛生部長阿扎，與台灣的衛福部長陳時中，就武漢肺炎疫情舉行電話會議，並違反一個中國原則，對此表示嚴重關切與堅決反對。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐聯合國日內瓦代表團發言人劉玉印表示，阿扎作為美國高官，公然與台灣官方接觸，並聲稱將全力支持台灣加入世衛，嚴重違反一中原則及中美三個聯合公報，將防疫議題政治化，向台獨勢力發出嚴重錯誤信號。<br />\n<br />\n劉玉印強調，台灣是中國的一部分，台灣參與國際組織，必須按一中原則處理，批評民進黨頑固堅持台獨分裂立場，拒不承認「九二共識」，導致台灣參加世衛大會的政治基礎不復存在，中方敦促有關國家認清形勢，恪守一中原則，停止借疫情操弄涉台問題。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523945-20200503.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523945-20200503.htm&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgt8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=63d70605\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523945-20200503.htm&h=1e4380f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523945-20200503.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5c0f0a9dc6723a8ed75091d1be243c14402f1efa","tid":1999003,"uid":258578,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T23:55:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f1fcf1f367fc66d737029c5c876b4718f1a8a6a","tid":1999003,"uid":2192,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T23:56:06.000Z","msg":"好似日日都loop緊同一單新聞咁，個日期就日日改<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e4b3dcc0677ffc14c469349afa88fa3b2967d47","tid":1999003,"uid":5005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T00:00:52.000Z","msg":"丁蟹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f2b887e58cafa814f026d91be906ec1f600856c","tid":1999003,"uid":13268,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T00:01:0